# Dependencies — keep full node_modules in VSIX (known-working baseline
# from v0.2.78 era). esbuild externalizes better-sqlite3 (native binary),
# linguist-js + skott (dynamic path resolution); all three need to be
# resolvable at runtime. Slim packaging experiments in v0.2.79..v0.2.85
# repeatedly broke activation. Reverted to full include.

